title: Quarkus 2.9.1.Final released - Maintenance release
content: It is my pleasure to announce the availability of Quarkus 2.9.1.Final, the first maintenance release of our 2.9 release. It is a safe upgrade for anyone already using 2.9. If you are not using 2.9 already, please refer to the 2.9 migration guide. Full changelog You can get the full...
